# SvelteKit conventions

## Routing & data
- Prefer `+page.server.ts` / `+layout.server.ts` for privileged data.
- Keep `load` functions focused; move heavy logic into `/src/lib/server` modules.

## Form actions
- Prefer form actions for mutations; validate input and return typed failure states.

## Components
- Keep components presentational; push domain logic into `/src/lib`.
